		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A cleric whose faith encourages misleading others. Sometimes, a deceiver will focus on tricking enemies in a way to protect people, and sometimes they follow self-centered doctrines that encourage them to lie and steal for their own benefit.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Deceiver</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.SoP28NqZhoDIQPBN]{Deceiver's Gift}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.WiEPMKO3u2DmzPHK]{Shadow Refuge}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.gyrFVTCBibVA2z1S]{Shroud of Darkness}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.nTgeLf9KkvZcruJo]{Trickster's Misdirection}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>Improved Trickster's Misdirection</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.09njGBRLUSKIl0i5]{Last Laugh}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Cleric Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.ABHn2WLXhBoSTYRl]{Color Spray}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.mcpWUlgl737AIttd]{Disguise Self}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.7dewwmP7KmxvlfKf]{Darkness}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.vWQiuirTFxetH3lm]{Invisibility}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.TmZ22s2pzXuzMX7n]{Hypnotic Pattern}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.726nL4N0WCfd9CRx]{Nondetection}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.w2ZlHcSOGX9EgYz0]{Greater Invisibility}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.bVLJ0ANP3MIhT5np]{Shadow Clone}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.cYHN8rl47RcgXPxL]{Mislead}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.qYulZxCoQoJXq730]{Seeming}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
